data.description: Perfect entry level 3 bedroom 2 bathroom and a bonus room. This home features high ceilings, granite counter tops, and an open floor plan that is perfect for entertaining.  Located near the foothills of Rosamond, there is easy access to restaurants, shopping, the freeway, and schools.  The backyard has a covered patio with potential for an owner to design their own oasis.
